CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper April 28, 1945, pg. 26, reads: "Swim Champs - Poised for the plunge are members of the Centre Avenue YMCA swimming team, winners of the Metropolitan Swimming Championship. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Centre Avenue YMCA swim team members, possibly including Pomeroyal Fountain wearing Pitt t-shirt on right, standing around corner of swimming pool
